      "q": "What is the exchange policy?",
      "a": "You can request an exchange within 7 days of receipt, provided the product is in its original condition."
    },
    "q2": {
      "q": "How can I track my order?",
      "a": "You can track your order through the My Orders section in your account."
    },
    "q3": {
      "q": "What payment methods are available?",
      "a": "We accept cash on delivery and Sham Cash."
    },
    "q4": {
      "q": "How long does delivery take?",
      "a": "Delivery takes 2-5 working days depending on the area."
    },
    "q5": {
      "q": "Can I cancel my order?",
      "a": "You can cancel your order before it is shipped by contacting us."
    },
    "q6": {
      "q": "How do I join the loyalty program?",
      "a": "With every purchase you earn points that you can use to get discounts."
    }
